      "width": 460,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Bullseye Authority Model\n\nTreat the visible graph as a bullseye centered on the focused fragment. Authority and detail fall off with distance from focus. Dictionaries can remain available for views while execution stays bounded.",
