      "width": 340,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Center Ring\n\nThe focused fragment has:\n- highest semantic detail\n- maximum authority\n- active execution context\n- normal dictionary + runtime behavior\n\nThis is the only region where code is allowed to run by default.",
