      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## First Ring\n\nDirectly linked `.node` graphs render at medium detail.\n\nPolicy:\n- load dictionary/view metadata needed to render\n- no execution authority\n- no remote code execution\n- no manifest takeover\n\nThese graphs support reading, not control.",
