      "width": 360,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Outer Ring\n\nMore distant linked graphs render at lower-detail views.\n\nPolicy:\n- load only the dictionary information required for the selected low-detail view\n- no execution authority\n- no remote code execution\n- no document authority\n\nThis ring is contextual background, not an active runtime.",
